<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1090</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhè shì yī gè sā huǎng de guó jiā, zhǔ a qiú nǐ lián mǐn.
 zhè shì yī gè bèi nì de mín zú, zhǔ a qiú nǐ lián mǐn.
 yīn zhe yé sū de yuán gù, yīn zhe shén ér zi liú xuè de jiù shú,
 yīn zhe nǐ ér nǚ zhòu yè de hū qiú, xiàng nǐ huǐ gǎi, cóng cǐ bì méng fú.</lyrics>
<title>zhǔ a qiú nǐ lián mǐn 迦南1090</title>
</song>